room_title: Escape room "Paranormal Investigation" by Get a Clue in Orange Beach
room_description: Poor ol' Mr. Johnson. Them ghosts he's been huntin' finally caught 'im in his own home. We talked last week and he'd said somethin' 'bout "appeasin'" 'em. Maybe if we found what he's been lookin' for, we can bring 'im back!
